                    <p>Our doctors provide general consultations for various health concerns, helping you understand your health and what actions to take.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h4>Specialized Treatment</h4>
                    <p>We offer specialized treatment across multiple fields, including cardiology, dermatology, and more, to ensure you get the best care.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h4>Emergency Care</h4>
                    <p>We are equipped with the resources to handle emergencies, ensuring timely medical intervention in critical situations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
